title: Cannot Enlist In Ocean Week
body:
The "Join Ocean Week" link in the client (Under "My Contribution".) brings me to the Ocean Week page http://promo.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/oceanweek2016/#join . However, nothing happened when the "Enlist Now" button is clicked.

Basically: 
On event website.
Clicked "Enlist Now".
A small "Join Ocean Week" screen popped up, with another "Enlist Now" button.
Clicked that and nothing happened.

I'm already logged in the website when the above happened.
